Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著大家再次降生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡等著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在流逝的時光中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻緊接一刻地死亡  一刻緊接一刻地轉生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從無到有的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:53.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:01:00.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:16.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:26.87,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:38.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:49.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:55.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:02:01.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:05.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.26,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:53.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:01:00.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在倒錯的精神世界中相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:16.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們眼裡的世界總是相互顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:26.87,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾乎要被認定為是無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:38.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口淌淚的眼眸 在內心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:49.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的兩人來不及結合便聽到離別的倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:55.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:02:01.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們像漸趨衰老的動物一樣相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:05.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在倒錯的精神世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想細細體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============OP=================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,390)\fs32\fad(600,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1B1B1B&\be5\blur2}愛的野獸們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 盡是些淡而無味的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那傢伙會在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是之前那野獸一般的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不經誕生禮節儀式之人不會有真正的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於自黑暗深淵中重生的他們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正好是恰當的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓女人全部退後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的目標是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這是性別歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是說這話的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是血肉之軀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想一下白刃戰的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我的洞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是墓穴特訓的成果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間填補
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合得如此默契
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心有靈犀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫唱婦隨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆轉之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他將填埋的力量轉換成了開辟的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢對我耍花招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你要對Mix做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 這傢伙也是香氣撲鼻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 他只對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來保護御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸井
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要妨礙我和臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋居然叫御子乃做臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連傷害都可以逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直率地朝向想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音…又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡做些奇怪的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在奏響大地與空氣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你那逆轉的不諧和音已經耳熟能詳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能被你妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人是只屬於…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一舉逆轉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野獸的猛攻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是一種有趣的音色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說他看上了御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人對一個女人窮追不舍的理由只有這一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 男人追男人也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據諸井發來的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以判斷那傢伙現正挾持著御子乃潛伏在市內
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就在地面進行搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兵分兩路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到那邊去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 我也跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人 你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 我只是要殺了你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你死在我的臂彎裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未影 你聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把氣味的源頭弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是使用方式有誤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未影你睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊已經完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽得很清楚啊 愛的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}未影 快讓我回來 未影 快回話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微讓我捉弄一下有何不可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰不會妒忌搶先得到心頭好的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃肯定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道? 知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他絕對不會加害於御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼那麼肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 他是御子乃命中注定的對像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃的真命天子不是阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聞到了 果然很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼你總是說出這麼過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我和你明明無怨無仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你一直待在Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 現在你在這裡把我殺掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我 在這種地方也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要我住手 那我就住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這根本就沒住手嘛 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想讓我舔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想…想殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是反語?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只對你說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…這雙眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺好令人懷念…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲 和我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前也這麼叫過我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲和阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話說的就是我們的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創世之初
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生命之樹下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偉大的生命之樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌管著該星球所有的生靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也掌管著星球自身的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在兩個種族的紛爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且給生命之樹授粉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 生命之樹的花朵卻沒有結出果實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼漸漸枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長此下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這星球將變成永無生命誕生的荒蕪之地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心相愛的阿波隆和希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護生命之樹而天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是希爾菲說道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕要等一萬兩千年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲 你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一萬兩千年之後再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…阿波隆的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…阿波隆?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想說御子乃就是希爾菲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會想出那麼荒謬的事情來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我無意中看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就能跟怪炎那喪服的婚禮的影像銜接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔也看過那影像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿波隆什麼的 希爾菲什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是個傳說而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當真能夠如此斷定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我稍微有點高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果御子乃和那傢伙真的是被命運所繫的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…阿馬塔和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡 你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:15:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了還在出沒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…我不是什麼希爾菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是…什麼希爾菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嚇我 希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糾纏不休的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有種能夠成功的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧特訓的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能把那傢伙的力量稍微抵銷一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如我所願 他沖著我這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來把將傢伙從御子乃身邊引開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趕快聯絡怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這樣不就成英雄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 是御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎說他馬上就過來支援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔你快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在御子乃成功逃脫之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得拖延住那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我去…死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死你 我要殺死你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屢次三番地…殺死你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要死了嗎 我…要死在這裡嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要陷入那黑暗的深淵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那黑暗之中…我又要變得孤身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔·空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗再也不是你為情所困而飽受煎熬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了斬斷如今的執著 締結新的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 把自己束縛在黑暗和孤獨之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄過去和執著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糾纏不休的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆向飛翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我的力量會不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無執著的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為一切外物所惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子是趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 不要掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我收拾掉他之前你就待在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 快給他最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是身處在以命相搏的立場上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開槍 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒這個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如象徵著復活的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不被允許的愛啊 儘管蘇醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越一萬兩千年的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------ED------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:59.44,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:07.25,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:17.23,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:26.73,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:34.59,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:42.18,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:46.37,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:49.53,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:54.06,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:57.27,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:24:01.60,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:08.11,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:59.44,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 點綴著雪白的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:07.25,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}從睡夢中驚醒之後 遠望著憂傷的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:17.23,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這份青澀的感覺 依存在綠葉錯綜的紋路之間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:26.73,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}側耳聆聽 晨露緩緩落下的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:34.59,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所創造的這個世界並不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:42.18,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因為這裡每天都有戀情一段接一段地告終
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:46.37,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初嘗戀愛的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:49.53,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這個你應該不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:54.06,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不見天日也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:57.27,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:24:01.60,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算你把我忘卻也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:08.11,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------ED------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.41,0:24:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我興奮並如此發酵的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.88,0:24:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一萬兩千年的命運的味道
